#: ../../custom_modules.rst:2
msgid "自定义模块"
msgstr "Custom Modules"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:4
msgid "AgentSociety 2 支持创建和注册自定义智能体和环境模块， 允许您使用自己的模拟组件扩展平台。"
msgstr ""
"AgentSociety 2 supports creating and registering custom agent and "
"environment modules, allowing you to extend the platform with your own "
"simulation components."

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:8
msgid "概述"
msgstr "Overview"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:10
msgid "自定义模块系统允许您："
msgstr "The custom module system allows you to:"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:12
msgid "创建具有专门行为的自定义智能体类"
msgstr "Create custom agent classes with specialized behaviors"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:13
msgid "创建具有特定领域工具的自定义环境模块"
msgstr "Create custom environment modules with domain-specific tools"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:14
msgid "通过 API 自动发现和注册模块"
msgstr "Automatically discover and register modules through API"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:15
msgid "使用自动生成的测试脚本测试自定义模块"
msgstr "Test custom modules with auto-generated test scripts"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:16
msgid "与现有 AgentSociety 框架无缝集成"
msgstr "Seamlessly integrate with existing AgentSociety framework"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:17
msgid "通过 Progressive Disclosure workflow 持久化需求、设计和验证产物"
msgstr ""
"Persist requirements, design, and validation artifacts through the "
"Progressive Disclosure workflow"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:20
msgid "目录结构"
msgstr "Directory Structure"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:22
msgid "自定义模块放置在工作区内的 ``custom/`` 目录中::"
msgstr ""
"Custom modules are placed in the ``custom/`` directory within your "
"workspace::"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:37
msgid "创建自定义智能体"
msgstr "Create Custom Agents"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:39
msgid ""
"所有自定义智能体必须继承 ``AgentBase``。智能体是 workspace 绑定的无状态 record：状态在 ``restore()``"
" 里恢复、在 ``to_workspace()`` 里写回；详见 :doc:`agents`。"
msgstr ""
"All custom agents must inherit from ``AgentBase``. Agents are workspace-"
"bound stateless records: state is restored in ``restore()`` and written "
"back in ``to_workspace()``; see :doc:`agents`."

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:79
msgid "必需方法"
msgstr "Required Methods"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:84 ../../custom_modules.rst:224
msgid "Method"
msgstr "Method"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:85 ../../custom_modules.rst:162
#: ../../custom_modules.rst:225
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Description"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:86
msgid "``mcp_description()``"
msgstr "``mcp_description()``"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:87
msgid "返回模块描述（类方法，建议覆盖；``AgentBase``/``EnvBase`` 有默认描述）"
msgstr ""
"Return module description (class method, recommended to override; "
"``AgentBase``/``EnvBase`` has default description)"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:88
msgid "``ask()``"
msgstr "``ask()``"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:89
msgid "回答环境的问题（必须实现）"
msgstr "Answer questions from the environment"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:90
msgid "``step()``"
msgstr "``step()``"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:91
msgid "执行一个模拟步骤（必须实现）"
msgstr "Execute one simulation step"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:92
msgid "``to_workspace()``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:93
msgid "把动态状态写回 workspace（必须实现）"
msgstr "Write dynamic state back to the workspace (required)."

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:94
msgid "``restore()``"
msgstr "``step()``"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:95
msgid "在 ``await super().restore(...)`` 之后恢复自定义状态（推荐覆盖）"
msgstr ""
"Restore custom state after ``await super().restore(...)`` (recommended "
"override)."

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:98
msgid "创建自定义环境"
msgstr "Create Custom Environments"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:100
msgid "自定义环境必须继承 ``EnvBase`` 并使用 ``@tool`` 装饰器注册方法："
msgstr ""
"Custom environments must inherit from ``EnvBase`` and use the ``@tool`` "
"decorator to register methods:"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:136
msgid "现实兼容约束"
msgstr "reality compatibility constraints"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:138
msgid "生成的自定义环境模块仍然必须遵循当前仓库的真实兼容约束："
msgstr ""
"The generated custom environment module must still follow the actual "
"compatibility constraints of the current repository:"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:140
msgid "文件必须位于 ``custom/envs/*.py``"
msgstr "File must be located at ``custom/envs/*.py``"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:141
msgid "类定义必须直接位于该文件中，不能只做 re-export"
msgstr ""
"The class definition must be located directly in this file, it cannot "
"just be re-exported"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:142
msgid "注册 key 继续使用 ``class_name``"
msgstr "Register key to continue using ``class_name``"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:143
msgid "至少存在一个合法 ``@tool``"
msgstr "There is at least one legal ``@tool``"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:144
msgid "``step()`` 必须存在"
msgstr "``step()`` must be present"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:145
msgid "默认应支持无参实例化 ``cls()``"
msgstr "Parameterless instantiation should be supported by default ``cls()``"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:146
msgid "若模块需要观察能力，应提供 ``@tool(readonly=True, kind='observe')`` 观察工具"
msgstr ""
"If the module needs observation capability, provide an "
"``@tool(readonly=True, kind='observe')`` observation tool"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:147
msgid "建议提供信息完整的 ``mcp_description()`` ；未覆盖时会显示基类默认描述"
msgstr ""
"Providing an informative ``mcp_description()`` is recommended; if not "
"overridden, the base class default description is displayed"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:151
msgid "扫描器会跳过路径中包含 ``examples/`` 的文件（示例仅供参考，不参与注册）。"
msgstr ""
"The scanner will skip files containing ``examples/`` in the path (the "
"example is for reference only and does not participate in registration)."

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:154
msgid "@tool 装饰器"
msgstr "@tool Decorator"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:156
msgid "``@tool`` 装饰器将方法注册为智能体可访问的工具："
msgstr "The ``@tool`` decorator registers methods as tools accessible to agents:"

