#: ../../custom_modules.rst:278
msgid "最佳实践"
msgstr "Best Practices"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:280
msgid "**命名约定**"
msgstr "**Naming Conventions**"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:282
msgid "智能体类名应以 ``Agent`` 结尾"
msgstr "Agent class names should end with ``Agent``"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:283
msgid "环境类名应以 ``Env`` 结尾"
msgstr "Environment class names should end with ``Env``"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:284
msgid "文件名应使用小写字母和下划线：``my_agent.py``"
msgstr "File names should use lowercase letters and underscores: ``my_agent.py``"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:286
msgid "**错误处理**"
msgstr "**Error Handling**"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:288
msgid "返回有意义的错误消息"
msgstr "Return meaningful error messages"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:289
msgid "对关键路径保留必要日志，便于复盘与定位问题"
msgstr ""
"Keep necessary logs on critical paths to facilitate review and problem "
"location."

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:291
msgid "**状态管理**"
msgstr "**State Management**"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:293
msgid "使用 ``restore()`` 从 workspace 恢复状态，使用 ``to_workspace()`` 写回动态状态"
msgstr ""
"Use ``restore()`` to restore state from the workspace and "
"``to_workspace()`` to write dynamic state back."

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:294
msgid ""
"自定义 Agent 覆盖 ``restore()`` 时应先调用 ``await super().restore(...)``，以绑定 "
"workspace、技能运行时和服务句柄"
msgstr ""
"When a custom Agent overrides ``restore()``, it should first call ``await"
" super().restore(...)`` to bind the workspace, skill runtime, and service"
" handles."

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:295
msgid "在回放中记录重要的状态更改"
msgstr "Record important state changes in replay"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:296
msgid "保持状态可序列化（JSON 兼容）"
msgstr "Keep state serializable (JSON compatible)"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:298
msgid "**工具设计**"
msgstr "**Tool Design**"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:300
msgid "对只读观察使用 ``kind=\"observe\"``"
msgstr "Use ``kind=\"observe\"`` for read-only observations"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:301
msgid "对聚合数据使用 ``kind=\"statistics\"``"
msgstr "Use ``kind=\"statistics\"`` for aggregated data"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:302
msgid "对操作使用 ``kind=None`` 和 ``readonly=False``"
msgstr "Use ``kind=None`` and ``readonly=False`` for operations"

#: ../../custom_modules.rst:303
msgid "生成后优先通过 workflow 产物中的 ``validation_report.json`` 定位失败原因"
msgstr ""
"After generation, priority is given to locating the failure reason "
"through ``validation_report.json`` in the workflow product."
